= Mail To

MailTo is a [Radiant CMS][1] extension that hides e-mails from robots. It is a simple wrapper for the [Rails mail_to tag][2] with :encode => :javascript.

= `mail_to`
The `mail_to` tag obfuscates an as a block of javascript. For example, 

	<r:mail_to/>
	
is turned into

	<script type="text/javascript">
	</script>
	
and will be output by web browsers as a human readable



= Acknowledgments


[1]: http://radiantcms.org/
[2]: http://api.rubyonrails.org/classes/ActionView/Helpers/UrlHelper.html#M001606
